name: Spirit of Chaos
effect:
1 "Magician of Black Chaos" or 1 Ritual monster that mentions "Dark Magician"

Must first be Fusion Summoned by sending the above card from your hand or field to the GY (you do not use "Polymerization").
This card’s name becomes "Dark Magician" while on the field or in the GY.
If this card is Special Summoned: You can add 1 Continuous Spell that mentions "Dark Magician" from your Deck or GY to your hand.
You can only activate this effect of "Spirit of Chaos" once per turn.
